skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: alexandria guide
des: Discover Alexandria, Virginia with this guide. Whether this is your first trip or you have visited many times before there is always something interesting to explore in Alexandria. Begin by opening the Alexandria Guide and asking for an overview of Alexandria. You can also ask for the top five things to do or for an attraction. For a complete list of options ask the guide for help.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
